no sound at all after the discovery of the european martian small hunting dog
( agence france - presse , london , 1 st ) spokesman for mars exploration program barte said u . s . satellites are unable to link up with u . 2 european little hunter - hunting dogs that have already landed on mars . they intend to collect signals from u . 2 . s . hunting dogs . now they can only pin hopes on their mother mars express .
balad said , " we have not got any more results . "
he said , " we have now placed our hope on its mother mars express vehicle for intelligence collection . "
the us mars odyssey spacecraft failed to receive any information yesterday from the european space survey little hunter ii that the little hunter ii has continued to search for life signs on mars since it departed from mars by express train .
the mars odyssey spacecraft was launched by the us space agency into mars for another exploration mission .
the european space agency , based in paris , said that the european - made mars satellite had already been launched into an extreme orbit , hoping it could send back some signals next week .
puerto landed on mars originally scheduled on the 2 nd , but its signals are still hard to detect .
on december 19 th , little hunter has become the first european spaceship to land on another star after leaving the mother ship mars express .
during the 18 - day flight mission , the little hunter ii plans to test the rocks , soil , signals transmission modes from mars , or all current life on mars .
scientists had boldly predicted that this british spaceship could be sunk in a hole .
pakistani president musharraf wins confidence vote in senate and house of representatives
( afp , islamabad , january 1 ) pakistani president musharraf today won the confidence vote of both the senate and the house of representatives amid islamic fundamentalists ' abstentions and opposition resistance . this confidence vote confirmed musharraf 's rule will last until 2007 .
" musharraf has won the majority vote in parliament , " information minister rashid told afp .
no congressmen voted against him . "
in the 342 - seat house of representatives , 191 members of the house of representatives voted to support musharraf , islamic fundamentalists abstaining from voting , and the opposition parties boycotted the controversial confidence vote .
musharraf has made concessions to six muslim parties , agreeing to resign as army commander - in - chief and to win the supreme court 's approval within one month after the dissolution of parliament .
in the 100 - seat senate , 56 senators voted to support musharraf , 42 muslim fundamentalists and opposition congressmen abstain from voting on or boycotting him .
musharraf won the political power in the october 1999 coup and has since refused to step down .
