( agence france - presse , puelung puerto , burundi , 1 st ) - in his new year 's day speech to the people of the whole country today , burundi 's president nundzye said the post - war joint chiefs of staff will be formed by next week , including former leaders of the anti - japanese armed forces .
the former rebel " democratic security army " welcomed the move and praised it as " an important step " towards the establishment of a new armed forces .
in a televised speech , president ndato said the rebels in the civil war in burundi over the past 10 years have to finish by january 5 , and the new leadership will be ready by january 7 , four of them will become the former rebel leaders .
" all parties to the ( november 2003 cease - fire ) agreement must complete the location of the soldiers by january 5 at the latest , " ndato said .
he added that the joint chiefs of staff , including former anti - japanese army leaders , must be ready by 7 january .
the operation was mainly related to the " democratic security army , " the largest of the six anti-fascist army organizations to sign a peace agreement .
the seventh anti-japanese army " national liberation army " refused to sign a peace agreement .
about 300,000 people have been killed since the 1993 civil war between the hutu anti - japanese army and tutsi government forces .
china detain 186 tons of us beef
( agence france - presse , beijing , 2nd ) - china 's state - run media , beijing qingnian bao , reported today that authorities concerned began to inspect the market of imported beef with the fear of being infected with the mad cow disease . they seized 186 tons of u . s . beef yesterday in beijing .
according to the ministry of agriculture 's proposal , the beef will be destroyed after testing , the paper said .
more than 30 countries in the world suspended imports of us beef last week , and china was one of them .
except for milk and other dairy products , and open - glucose solution used for leather and photography , all products related to the cattle are subject to a ban .
the beijing agricultural bureau has recently issued a series of regulations on prevention and control and supervision , and launched comprehensive market inspection , the beijing youth daily reported .
there are no cases of mad cow disease in all parts of china .
earlier , authorities detained 60 kilograms of us beef from a us cargo ship in ningbo , zhejiang province , the second of its kind in the week .
china 's imports of meat from the united states amounted to 532 million dollars last year , but imports of us beef remained unclear , the commerce department said tuesday .
from january to july last year , china imported a total of 316 million us dollars ' worth of meat .
