the international thermonuclear experimental reactor project will be built at qatar or at six villages in northern japan 's qingsenlin county .
the plan aims to provide a laboratory simulating the phenomenon of solar nuclear fusion , which is known as the least clean , safe and inexhaustible source of future energy .
