katsav said on israel 's public radio earlier today : " i have invited albanian president aliyev to come to jerusalem to seriously negotiate with israeli leaders on the various conditions for the peace agreement . "
katsav added , " azerbaijan will be welcomed , but should not set preconditions . "
in an interview with cnn , syrian overseas chinese affairs minister shban said that israel must make it clear that it is willing to resume negotiations with a breakdown in consultation four years ago .
khaleda zia 's move was not a " serious response " to president aliyev 's appeal last month for the restoration of contacts with israel . he also accused president katsav of only trying to win the media 's exposure .
the syrian official news agency salem , quoted an unnamed senior official as saying that the israeli president intends to bypass the land - for - peace process in the middle east .
the official said : " this visit or the issue of taking the initiative . israel 's recent remarks were aimed at avoiding the peace process . "
the official added : " some of the solutions and measures can not bring peace to the middle east region . "
in previous negotiations with the late father of azerbaijan , the then israeli prime minister barretk agreed to nearly completely withdraw from the golan heights , only retaining a narrow corridor adjacent to the east coast of galilee sea .
damascus , however , refuses to accept the proposal , and hopes that israel will return to the golan heights , which was occupied in the 1967 war and acquired in 1981 .
