ross told the newspaper : " in the afternoon , i was on a break at home . some people knocked on my house . i saw two white staff members of the tolucci company from the door hole . they wanted to talk to me about the boxing tournament . "
" we have brought some money to you and we are not on the verge . they hope i will release water in the competition and tell me not to defeat vegetable beans . "
