the daily news in new york rushed to erekat 's residence in alabama to ask him if he believed ross in his statements . alxso was partial to and protected the tortutsk company . he said , " the force of ross did not match . how could you get a record of 1 / 6 boxing shooter out of water ? i do n't think tolucci would violate the law . "
