the contribution of the consumer council to consumer protection over the past three decades is obvious to all .
it would be best to assess the effectiveness of the consumer council 's work .
i agree with president chen that after 30 years , not only the consumers are aware of their own rights and interests , but all sectors of the community also attach importance to the rights and interests of consumers , which is the fruit of the efforts of the consumer council and the government .
the consumer council regularly conducts testing on the products and conducts market surveys and research on the operation of various products and services , and releases fair and objective market information to the public through the " choice " magazine .
the " selection " magazine is deeply trusted by the public . now that the " choice " magazine develops its internet version , it will play a more effective role in helping consumers obtain market information more easily .
the consumer council has 11 district consumer advisory centres and 16 telephone hotlines to provide information on goods and services to consumers and to receive complaints from consumers .
since its establishment , the number of enquiries received by the consumer council has increased from several thousand in the early 1970 s to 146,000 last year , an increase of more than 20 times , indicating that more and more consumers will make reference to the consumer council 's report and advice before choosing their products and services .
in addition , the consumer council handled more than 26,000 complaints this year .
the consumer council will also recommend individual shops with unscrupulous practices , which will not only help consumers beware of swindlers , but also serve as a deterrent to traders .
