over the past several hundred years since the birth of the intellectual property system , especially since the industrial revolution , the birth of one major invention after another has epoch - making significance .
over the past 20 years , the intellectual property system has become a basic legal system and important policy means for various countries to promote technological innovation and has played an important role in invigorating the economy and enhancing their international competitiveness .
at present , with the rapid development of science , technology , and economic globalization , the creation , possession , and use of knowledge and intellectual resources and the quantity and quality of intellectual property have become an important foundation for various countries to participate in international competition .
therefore , international exchanges and cooperation for the protection of intellectual property is of great significance to the establishment of a fair and rational new international economic order and the promotion of world economic prosperity and development .
the chinese government attaches great importance to protecting intellectual property rights .
in the early stage of reform and opening up , china began to establish the intellectual property system . after more than 20 years of hard work , a relatively complete legal system for intellectual property rights has been formed , and a system for protecting intellectual property rights has been established in which judicial departments and administrative law enforcement are combined . china has done a lot of work in protecting intellectual property rights and has made important contributions to promoting scientific and technological progress and economic and social development .
as mankind enters the information society in the 21 st century , the revolution in science and technology will promote the development of social productive forces with an unprecedented , tremendous impetus .
further perfecting china 's intellectual property system and strengthening international exchanges and cooperation in ipr protection are required for china to open wider to the outside world in the new century , and are also needed for building a socialist modern country and achieving the great rejuvenation of the chinese nation .
we are willing to work together with other countries in the world to establish a fair and rational intellectual property system that is conducive to promoting scientific , technological , and economic development in various countries and to creating a fine environment for mankind to respect knowledge , advocate science , and protect intellectual property rights .
accelerating the establishment of a mechanism for organization building is the most important task facing the sco at present .
with the efforts of all parties concerned , the secretariat and the regional anti - terrorist organizations have made great progress in preparing for the construction .
we must make continued efforts to ensure that the secretariat will be formally activated this year and that a regional anti - terrorist agency will be set up at an early date .
