in the past year , the trend of economic globalization has continued to develop , and science and technology progress with each passing day has brought new development opportunities to various countries .
at the same time , uncertain factors in global economic development have increased , and some countries and regions , including apec members , are facing new challenges in the course of economic development .
trade protectionism is gaining ground , and achieving free , fair , and just trade remains a long - term and arduous task .
the struggle against terrorism is arduous and complex , and non - traditional security factors have increased .
our world is still far from tranquil .
although the international community is still faced with all kinds of problems and may also encounter all kinds of unexpected problems in the future , the tide of the times of peace and development is irreversible , and the aspirations of the people of all countries for a happy life remain unchanged .
it is of great significance that development is the theme of this dialogue .
development is the foundation for the progress of human civilization and the key to resolving various contradictions and problems facing the world .
only by achieving global coordination , balance , and universal development will it be possible to achieve lasting world peace and stability .
we should explore this issue in a comprehensive and in - depth manner and work with concerted efforts to resolve it .
the accelerated development of the trend of economic globalization has become the most prominent characteristic of the world economy today .
driven by the trend of economic globalization , ties between various countries and regions have become increasingly close , markets have become more open , and the flow of capital , technology , and talent has become more extensive and rapid . all this has brought unprecedented opportunities for strengthening international cooperation and promoting common development .
at the same time , the development trend of economic globalization has also brought serious challenges to the south - north gap . some developing countries are facing the danger of being further marginalized , increasing economic and financial risks , and serious transnational crime . all this has added to the urgency of carrying out international cooperation and jointly meeting challenges .
at this moment when opportunities and challenges coexist , we should seize the opportunities , meet the challenges , seek common ground while reserving differences , expand cooperation , and promote economic globalization in the direction of realizing common development and prosperity .
( international ) us flu spread to peak
xinhua news agency , los angeles , december 31 ( reporter yan liang ) the us centers for disease control and prevention said on the 31 st that the flu in the united states , which was rarely seen in more than 30 years , has reached its peak , and 45 of the 50 us states have seen a rather large - scale spread of flu , resulting in a rapid increase in the number of deaths caused by influenza .
according to statistics released by the center as of december 20 , the number of deaths caused by influenza in the united states has reached an all - time high of 7.8 percent for the same period .
at least 42 children died of influenza in the country , and cases of adult death are also on the rise , but it is not yet available for accurate statistics .
experts believe that there are two reasons for the serious spread of influenza in 2003 : one is that the flu virus is not a " panama - type " flu virus , which was prevalent in previous years , which has prevented effective vaccine from effectively preventing the virus ; the other is that last year , there was a surplus of flu vaccines in the united states , and the two major vaccine supplying companies reduced the output to 83 million vaccines this year , resulting in this year 's supply of vaccines .
although an average of 360,000 people in the united states die of influenza each year and 1.24 million people are hospitalized due to influenza , it is hardly anything that has led to a certain degree of social panic like this flu .
william thompson , an american pop expert , believes that influenza is the worst in the united states in nearly 30 years . moreover , it is even earlier than in previous years that influenza has spread in many schools and has been lined up in many places where flu vaccination has been given .
faced with such a grim situation , the us department of health activated an emergency handling center on 19 december and dispatched a medical expert group to various states .
two vehicles crash kills three in zhejiang
xinhua news agency , hangzhou , january 1 , a serious traffic accident occurred in ninghai county , zhejiang province , the morning of the 1 st .
due to the dense fog , seven people were killed and four others injured when an overloaded car and a large truck collided .
at about 2 : 00 a.m . on the 1 st , the driver , hua , drove a red flag brand taxi with a license plate number of zhejiang bo 8705 to the direction of ninghai , carrying six passengers .
at that time , the fog was in the air and the eyes were unclear .
when the two lanes were about 60 kilometers away , a taxi and a large truck carrying a total of 353.78 meters in the same direction collided .
it was learned that at that time , the large truck entered the main lane of the main traffic lane from above , while the taxi tried to avoid delay , bumped into the lower portion of the truck , seriously distorted the vehicle , and three of the seven people , including the driver , died on the spot .
after the accident occurred , the traffic police department of zhejiang province immediately issued a circular , demanding that the traffic police departments across the province immediately take measures to strengthen traffic management under bad weather conditions , prevent vehicles from overcarrying vehicles and speeding up accidents , and ensure road safety during the spring festival transportation period .
( international ) 14 more earthquake survivors rescued in iran
xinhua news agency , tehran , january 1 , iran 's state radio said on the 1 st that iranian search and rescue personnel found 14 more survivors in the ruins of the bam earthquake - stricken area on the 31 st and the 1 st .
" we have saved at least one life , " said ali ashirada , a staff member of the iranian red crescent society , when he rescued a young shop owner from a wardrobe on the 1st .
i have gone to the battlefield and experienced many tests , but i have never been so happy about it . "
iranian national radio said that search and rescue personnel also rescued a nine - year - old girl and a pregnant woman from the ruins .
their health is very poor .
according to a state radio report , rescue workers discovered 11 survivors on the 31 st , including a four - month - old baby and an 80 - year - old woman .
however , rescuers believe that with the passage of time , the chance of finding survivors is very slim .
according to statistics , the search and rescue personnel have found about 280,000 bodies at the scene of the earthquake and have buried some of the dead bodies .
in addition , they rescued 2,000 survivors from the ruins , and most of them were discovered the day after the earthquake occurred .
according to the latest report on iran 's earthquake disaster , the death toll from the earthquake is expected to rise to 34,000 , according to information collected from the earthquake - stricken areas and other channels , the united nations humanitarian coordination office said today .
( international ) americans greet new year through float parade and winter games
xinhua news agency , washington , january 1 , various celebration activities are being held in various parts of the united states to greet the arrival of the new year .
the most eye - catching ones are the annual " rose parade " in los angeles , california , and the winter games in minnesota .
on the same day , several hundred thousand tourists gathered in the streets of los angeles to watch the 115 th " roses float " parade . they felt the festive mood brought about by the new year amid the splendid performance of the band and the brilliant and colorful float parade .
in order to prevent terrorist activities , the los angeles police have adopted unprecedentedly tight security measures .
more than 1,000 policemen and plain clothes sneaked into the crowd to monitor suspects .
the police also used video cameras , helicopters , police dogs , and other measures to monitor the scene of the demonstration and carry out strict checks on suspicious items .
on the same day , about 100 vehicles parked near the procession route were searched by the police .
in the cold state of minnesota , about 500 people participated in the 14 th minnesota winter games to donate money to local charity groups .
the courageous act of swimming attracted a large crowd of spectators , winning unanimous applause and support from the participants .
( international ) foreign ministers of south asian countries discuss free trade area and anti - terrorism issues
xinhua news agency , islamabad , january 2 ( reporter zhang ning ) a two - day meeting of foreign ministers of the south asian regional cooperation alliance ( south asian union ) opened in islamabad on the 2nd . foreign ministers of member countries of the south african union will discuss such important issues as the establishment of a south asian free trade zone and the signing of an additional anti - terrorism protocol .
during the conference , the foreign ministers will also study specific ways of cooperation in curbing the trafficking of women and children , protecting the rights and interests of children , and setting up a foundation for the disabled .
hossei kasuri , pakistan 's minister of foreign affairs , was elected chairman of the conference .
in his speech , he called on member states of the south african union to strengthen cooperation and exchanges , enhance mutual understanding , and make joint efforts to safeguard peace and stability in the region so as to create conditions for eliminating poverty and promoting economic development in the region .
this meeting of foreign ministers of the south african union was the preparation for the south african union summit .
the 12th south african union summit will be held in islamabad from 4 to 6 january . heads of state or government of the seven member countries of the south african union , bangladesh , bhutan , the maldives , nepal , india , pakistan , and sri lanka will attend the meeting .
the south african union summit has drawn much attention because of speculation that leaders of india and pakistan may hold talks on bilateral relations during the summit .
( international ) us rescue team says aid to iran has no political color
xinhua news agency , bahrain ( iran ) ( by jiang xiaofeng , liao zhenyun ) - the humanitarian aid project director of the u . s . international development agency , steve kartin , who is taking part in the earthquake relief work in bba district of iran , said to xinhua reporters on the 2nd that u . s . rescue teams ' participation in the relief activities in iran does not have any political color .
karterin pointed out that the rescue team organized by the us side had " nothing to do with politics " and that the us had also offered similar humanitarian aid to iran in the past .
he said that the rescue team , made up of 84 people , set up a city search and rescue team and a battlefield hospital in the baham area , and several small teams were also responsible for assessing the damage of houses in the city .
they also brought in plastic film , tents , and other relief supplies .
asked how long the us rescue team would stay in barley , karterin said : " the owner ( the iranian government ) will stay for a long time . "
karterin also said that the us rescue team 's activities in bam were free and there was no iranian police to protect or track them .
in addition , he believes that the iranian government 's ability to respond to earthquakes and deal with disasters is " first - rate and outstanding " .
the us international development agency is a subordinate organ of the international development and cooperation agency and will be put under the administration of the us state department .
since the united states and iran severed diplomatic relations in 1980 , the two sides have not resumed normal relations .
the united states has so far still regarded iran as one of the " countries that support terrorism " and " centers of evil . "
the united states sent a rescue team to iran this time at the invitation of iran 's ambassador to the united nations .
( international ) israeli deputy prime minister denies plan to expand golan heights
xinhua news agency , london , january 2 israeli deputy prime minister olmert denied on the 2nd that israel plans to expand jewish settlements in the golan heights , saying that there is no such " plan " nor such a " policy . "
israeli agriculture minister kaz told the press on december 31 last year that the israeli government plans to double the number of jewish settlers residing in the golan heights before holding peace talks with syria , in order to strengthen its control of the golan heights .
olmert said in an interview with the bbc that the development of agriculture , tourism , and settlements on the golan heights was wrong .
he said : " i have repeatedly verified with the premier and the finance minister in the past two days . according to the government 's promise , there is no such approved plan . "
he said that although some ministers support such plans , the government will not give them support .
the golan heights was captured by israel in the third middle east war in 1967 by syria , and currently there are a total of 17,000 jewish settlers .
because of this , syria and israel have been in a state of war for a long time .
kaz 's remark on expanding the golan heights immediately aroused widespread concern in the international community . syria condemned israel 's plan for expansion and stressed that it was illegal .
china 's high - tech modern weapons industry begins to take shape
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 3 ( reporters li jinyan and li bin ) in the past year , the china ordnance group corporation , as one of china 's top 10 military industrial enterprises , has made major progress in the development and reform of new weaponry and equipment and in extricating itself from difficulties .
ma zhigeng , general manager of the china ordnance group corporation , said here on 3 march that the company had earned 49.7 billion yuan in sales in 2003 , an increase of 19.7 percent over the same period of last year . the whole system had turned around its losses and increased profits two years ahead of schedule , and the industry of high - tech modern weapons was already in its embryonic form in china .
the ordnance industry is china 's largest industry in the field of science , technology and industry for national defense , and is of fundamental strategic importance in the modernization of national defense .
in recent years , the china ordnance industry group corporation has persisted in being the leader in science and technology and the leader in personnel development . on the one hand , it has paid attention to the research and development of high - tech weapons . on the other hand , it has grasped the reform and turnaround of state enterprises and the large - scale operation of civilian products . it has successfully developed a number of new and high - tech weapons and equipment that the chinese army urgently needs , thus forming a number of high - tech military products
at the same time , the china ordnance group corporation has vigorously pushed ahead with structural adjustment and closed down 21 enterprises as a result of bankruptcy and bankruptcy . the total number of employees has been reduced from 60,000 during the period when the group company was founded to 360,000 . it has achieved a net reduction of 116,000 people and six enterprises have been reorganized and listed on the market .
( international ) mongolian livestock industry improves in 2003
xinhua news agency , ulan bator , january 5 ( reporter lu guodong ) according to local media reports on the 5 th , up from the end of 2003 , mongolia 's livestock stock was 2530.78 million head , an increase of 16.33 million over the same period last year .
this is the first time that the reserves of mongolian domestic animals have risen after falling for three consecutive years .
last summer , there was plenty of rain and no heavy snow in spring and winter , which created favorable conditions for improving the livestock industry in mongolia .
by the end of 2003 , china had 25.56 million camels , 195.83 million horses , 178.43 million cattle , 107.062 million sheep and 106.34 million goats .
compared with the same period last year , the number of camels , sheep and sheep has increased while the number of cattle and buffalos has decreased .
mongolia 's livestock industry was basically privatized in the 1990 s .
however , after privatization , the livestock industry was completely " relying on heaven for food . "
from 1994 to 1999 , mongolia 's livestock industry enjoyed six consecutive years of prosperity due to a smooth weather .
at the end of 1999 , mongolia 's livestock stock reached a record high of 33.5 million heads .
however , from 2000 to 2002 , mongolia suffered setbacks for three consecutive years in winter and summer droughts , and for three consecutive years for its livestock industry .
at the end of 2002 , the number of mongolian domestic animals stored was 236,845 , a drop of 99.55 million in three years .
( international ) dprk says it will use military force against united states
xinhua news agency , pyongyang , january 6 ( reporter ji xinlong ) the central news agency of the democratic people 's republic of korea ( dprk ) issued a commentary on the 6th , demanding that the united states respond with goodwill to the dprk 's efforts to resolve the nuclear issue . it also said that the dprk would vigorously strengthen its military strength and use military force against the united states .
the commentary said : to ease tension on the korean peninsula and ensure peace and stability on the korean peninsula , the most important thing is to peacefully resolve the nuclear issue between the dprk and the united states through dialogue .
the dprk has put forward a package plan based on the principle of simultaneous action .
the commentary reiterated that the peaceful resolution of the nuclear issue through dialogue has been the dprk 's consistent principled stand .
the us government should treat this stand of the dprk with goodwill .
however , the weapons and other advanced weapons that the united states is going to test in the afghanistan and iraq battlefields will be transported into south korea soon , and preparations for a new war are being accelerated .
the commentary also said : " with regard to the dprk 's hardline policy of comprehensively negating and threatening its ideology and system , the dprk will deal with it with it with super strong resolve . " this is a self-defense choice that the dprk should adopt to defend its sovereignty and its survival rights and safeguard peace and stability on the korean peninsula and in the region .
the greater the united states ' threat , the more the dprk will further strengthen its anti - imperialist military front and use its military force against the united states .
( international ) us service industry still lagging behind manufacturing industry
xinhua news agency , new york , january 6 ( reporter xue yanping ) a report released by the supply management association of well - known us research institutions on the 6 th showed that the index of service industry in the united states fell in april last year , indicating that the growth of service industry is still lagging behind the manufacturing industry .
the report said that the index of service industries , including retail , financial , construction and other non - manufacturing sectors , dropped from 60.1 in the previous month to 58.6 in december , and economists had estimated that the index would rise to 60.5 .
according to the standards set by the supply management association , the index of service industries is higher than 50 represented by the expansion of the industry , and less than 50 represented a contraction in the industry .
the index of manufacturing output in the united states rose to its highest level in 20 years , according to a report released by the supply management association on tuesday .
this shows that the growth of the us service industry is still lagging behind the manufacturing industry .
the growth of the manufacturing industry is conducive to expanding employment and promoting economic growth , but the growth of the service industry plays an even greater role in reducing unemployment and promoting economic growth .
( international ) li zhaoxing , pakistani foreign minister talk over phone to congratulate south african union summit
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 7 , visiting chinese foreign minister li zhaoxing made a phone call on pakistan 's foreign minister kasuri on the 6 th to warmly congratulate the success of the south asian regional cooperation alliance ( south african union ) summit in islamabad .
li zhaoxing said : the important document adopted by the current meeting has set the development goal for the south african union . it will promote the cause of peace and development in the region and conforms to the interests of the people of all south asian countries .
as a friendly neighbor , china sincerely hopes that south asia will maintain peace and stability and advance toward prosperity .
china is willing to work together with all south asian countries , including pakistan , to promote peace and development in the region .
li zhaoxing said : during the meeting , pakistani and indian leaders met with each other and reiterated that they would take further measures to ease the tension in relations .
the chinese side welcomes and supports this and is willing to make its own contribution to promoting peace and development in south asia .
kasuri spoke highly of the constructive role played by china in promoting peace and development in south asia .
