first company health quarantine for incoming and outgoing drivers implemented in shenzhen
xinhua news agency , shenzhen , january 8 ( li nanling ) in order to effectively prevent the spread of atypical pneumonia through shenzhen 's ports and protect people 's health , the shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau recently issued a public notice , deciding to implement health quarantine measures for drivers entering and leaving the three land ports at huanggang , man kam to and sha tau kok from the 9 th day .
it has been learned that since there are many vehicles traveling from shenzhen to and from the mainland , such as the average number of vehicles traveling to and from the mainland at huanggang control point is 25,000 vehicles per day , it is quite difficult to ensure smooth flow at the man kam to control point and to carry out health quarantine checks on all drivers .
in order to do a good job in temperature screening and health quarantine application , the shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has overcome all kinds of difficulties . in addition to increasing the number of additional personnel internally to the front line of the control point , it recently also urgently hired more than 250 people to work on the front line after conducting centralized training to ensure the safety and smooth flow of ports . at the same time , it also bought 60 more portable infrared rapid temperature monitoring devices .
the shenzhen inspection and quarantine bureau has asked all relevant units and drivers of entry and exit passengers to pay attention to the fact that the " entry - exit health quarantine application card " can be obtained from the work spot or temperature check point of the " inspection and quarantine book for imported and exported vehicles and goods ( personnel ) " from the inspection and quarantine departments at all ports .
at the same time , the bureau called on relevant units and drivers of exit and entry to work together to do a good job in this work , effectively prevent the spread of sars through shenzhen port , and protect people 's health .
( international ) u.s. dollar hits low
xinhua news agency , new york , january 8 , under the influence of a speech by the governor of the european central bank , the dollar edged down again eight days after a flash in the pan on the 7 th .
the president of the european central bank , jean - claude trichet , issued a commentary on the same day , saying that the excessively high euro exchange rate had a negative impact on the export of european enterprises , but he believed that the gradual recovery of the world economy and the brisk growth of consumer demand had partly offset the impact of the euro 's appreciation .
he also pointed out that the strong euro had played a positive role in the price stability of the euro zone to a certain extent , so the european central bank decided to maintain the original interest rate level .
investors took the comments as a signal that euro - zone officials were not worried about the euro 's appreciation , and sold the dollar one after another , leading to a lower dollar against other major currencies in the west . the pound sterling rose to an 11 - year high .
at the close of new york foreign exchange on the 8th , the euro against the us dollar fell from 1.2640 to 1.2761 , the british pound against the us dollar at one point to 1.8534 from 1.8180 , the us dollar against the japanese yen at one point to 106.17 yen , and the swiss franc rate from 1.2398 to 1.2267 .
