he disclosed that because brazil has implemented measures to capture fingerprints and photography of americans , about 320 americans have canceled their travel plans to brazil .
the us government decided last year to implement measures to take photographs and draw fingerprints of foreigners , including brazilian citizens , into the united states from january 5 this year .
in order to protest against the us move , the brazilian government has also taken the same measure against americans entering the country since 1 january .
the us government has expressed dissatisfaction over brazil 's practice on many occasions .
