( international ) two black boxes of passenger planes found in red sea accident
xinhua news agency , cairo , january 17 , egypt and france recovered the first black box of the passenger plane in the red sea on the 16 th , and found the second black box from the plane that crashed deep down the sea .
the head of the egyptian search and rescue team hammadi said that the french submarine " sky scorpion " was salvage the second black box recording the noise of the pilot 's cabin , and it is expected to salvage water early on the 18th local time .
the two black boxes were found 100 to 100 meters underwater , about 30 meters apart .
shakeda [ name as transliterated ] , head of the egyptian investigation committee on accidents , said that the first black box recorded various technical data before the crash . the black box will be " deciphered and analyzed " by the egyptian civil aviation laboratory .
although the black box seems to have been seriously damaged , jatislava said that it is " in good condition . "
the two so - called black boxes on the plane appeared in fact light yellow .
according to the design , they can send signals for 30 days after falling 6,000 meters deep to ensure that the search and rescue personnel determine their positions and carry out salvage .
the passenger plane that crashed in the red sea area belongs to the egyptian private flakes company .
the boeing 737 passenger plane crashed into the red sea shortly after taking off from sharm el sheikh , egypt , on 3 may , killing 148 people , including 134 french , one morrison , and 13 egyptian crew members .
experts from egypt and france said the air crash came from a technical malfunctioning rather than a terrorist attack or explosion and the discovery of two black boxes on board would help undetected the mystery .
china has achieved breakthrough in preserving and replanting technology
xinhua news agency , jinan , january 18 ( reporters su wanming and su wanming ) the broken finger that was successfully preserved in the form of antiwarm nitrogen at 96 degrees celsius had been successfully planted during the operation .
a few days ago , chinese scholars announced that they had achieved a major breakthrough in the maintenance and replanting of the bollworm temperature .
a few days ago , the hand surgery department of shandong 's provincial hospital once again successfully carried out a broken index for a patient ( which had been successfully replanted for five days in the v 196 degrees celsius liquid nitrogen ) . this is the second successful operation of the hospital since the operation ( preserving 81 days in liquefied nitrogen ) last year .
the new consultation report of the medical science and technology project of the ministry of public health confirmed that there were only two successful cases in the world that the broken finger bone relic was preserved so far .
wang zengtao , director of the hand surgery department of shandong provincial hospital , said : " after a great deal of animal experiments and research and the clinical applications of two cases , we have initially mastered the technique of killing people and preserving them . "
wang zengtao said : compared with organs such as heart and kidney , the composition and structure of fingers are more complicated , including various kinds of organizations such as blood vessels , nerve , myths , skin , bones , key links , and tenths , and they are a compound organization .
as for the preservation and application of skin heat , they pointed out that it was a series of complicated links in the prevention and treatment of damages caused by freezing and retaining fluid , organ freezing procedures , restoration of temperature , replanting , and replanting .
the mastery of this technology has provided important lessons for relevant research such as the long - term preservation and successful recovery of the skin temperature of other human organs .
( international ) greek foreign minister calls on greece , turkey to reduce military spending
xinhua news agency , athens , january 17 ( reporter wen xinnian ) - greek foreign minister and president of the ruling pan - greece socialist movement papandreou on the 17th called on greece and turkey to gradually reduce their military spending according to their proportion .
he said that if the pan - greek social movement wins the general election on march 7 , he would take this policy as an important foreign policy of the government .
speaking at a mass rally prior to his departure for the eastern part of greece , papandreou said relations between greece and turkey had improved significantly in recent years and had entered a new historical period .
he said : although not all problems have been resolved , new conditions have been created and the road of negotiations has been established .
he believes that 2004 will be of decisive significance to the formulation of regional peace and security policies .
both greece and turkey are members of nato . however , there are conflicts of interests and contradictions between the two sides on the demarcation of the aegean sea and the continental shelf and on cyprus and other issues , which have also affected the normalization of relations between the two countries .
in recent years , greece has pursued a policy of improving relations with turkey and stopped turkey from joining the european union .
