( international ) us troops killed three non - iraqi arabs in iraq
xinhua news agency report of january 19 from baghdad ( by staff reporters li jizhi and nie xiaoyang ) - the iraqi police disclosed on the 19 th that two equal persons and one syrian were killed in a weapons search operation conducted by us troops in the southern suburbs of baghdad that day .
police said that the us military found these three people during its search of the " hideout of the terrorists " . when the other side refused to surrender , the us troops opened fire and killed three people .
the us military searched the house afterwards and found some rifles , hand grenades , and explosives .
the us military also arrested a yemeni woman at the scene .
us and iraqi officials believe that some foreign religious extremists are entering iraq through the border of loose defense and are colluding with anti - american forces in iraq to launch terrorist attacks on coalition occupation authorities and pro - us iraqi people .
on the 18th , a suicide attacker exploded a powerful car bomb at the entrance of the coalition headquarters in central baghdad , killing 24 people and injuring over 100 , and most of the victims were iraqis .
( international ) jobless rate in silicon valley shows signs of recovery of us high - tech industries
xinhua news agency , los angeles , january 19 ( reporter yan liang ) an influential economic development research institute in the silicon valley in the united states recently released a report saying that the unemployment rate in silicon valley is rapidly declining .
this is a clear signal that high - tech industries in this region have started to recover .
in its annual report entitled " silicon valley : 2004 economic index , " a non-profit organization said that the unemployment rate in silicon valley from the second quarter of 2002 to the second quarter of 2003 dropped from 10 percent in the previous year to 5 percent .
the report said that the unemployment rate will continue to decline as high - tech industries gradually recover .
the challenge facing the development of the silicon valley today is that it requires a large number of highly trained high - tech workers to fill new jobs in the future .
the report said that among the various high - tech industries in silicon valley , the unemployment rate is the lowest , and the momentum of recovery is also the most obvious . the amount of risk investment attracted by the biotechnology industry in silicon valley in 2003 is the first time similar to the computer software industry .
the report holds that biotechnology industry will play an increasingly important role in the economic development of silicon valley .
the report also showed that the average salary for employees in silicon valley between the second quarter of 2002 and the second quarter of 2003 fell for the third consecutive year , but the rate of decline has dropped from 6 percent in the previous year to 1.5 percent .
silicon valley is still a prosperous region in the united states . the average annual salary of the labor force in this region is 624,000 us dollars , 60 percent higher than the average level in the whole country .
however , the consumption level of this region is 47 percent higher than that of the whole country .
( hong kong , macao and taiwan ) chief executive of the hong kong special administrative region tung chee hwa delivers his lunar new year message
xinhua news agency , hong kong , january 21 , " the sky begins , the earth transforms into new planes . "
on the eve of the lunar new year , tung chee - hwa , chief executive of the hong kong special administrative region , and his wife betty tung delivered a congratulatory message on television , radio , and the internet , wishing hong kong and the people of hong kong success in their new year .
tung chee - hwa said that this year 's spring festival is particularly meaningful and joyful for the people of hong kong .
having experienced a number of years of difficulties , hong kong 's economy has rebounded , unemployment has dropped , deflation has eased , the property market has stabilized , and the most intimate economic and trade arrangements with the mainland have begun to take effect , coupled with the surge in tourists and the buoyant consumer market .
tung chee - hwa said : " what is more gratifying is that our efforts over the years have laid a good foundation for further promoting hong kong 's economic restructuring and development . "
he expressed the hope that everyone will have a smooth new year in everything .
tung chee - hwa said that the hong kong community has reached a consensus on the new direction , and everyone is facing new opportunities one after another .
the new year is the monkey .
the " monkey " is acute and full of vitality .
as long as the government and the people of hong kong continue to work hard and with the staunch support of the central government , hong kong will certainly be able to run the whole world .
( international ) arab league secretary general calls on us not to impose " democracy " on middle east
xinhua news agency , geneva , january 21 , secretary general moussa of the league of arab states ( arab league ) urged the united states on the 21 st to discuss democracy with arab countries instead of trying to impose democracy on the middle east region .
moussa said in an interview with reporters during the annual meeting of the world economic forum held in davos , switzerland , " if they ( americans ) want to achieve democracy in the middle east , they would have better honor their commitments and would first achieve democracy in iraq . "
he said : the league of arab states is the best partner to discuss with the united states the issue of democratic reform in the middle east region .
" so long as you express your views and are willing to listen to our views , everything can be discussed .
we do not oppose democracy , but democracy is not an immediate action or order . "
moussa pointed out that the us government has yet to make people believe that occupation of iraq will bring " democracy " to this country .
" they said that their visit to iraq was for the purpose of showing us a model of democracy that we can imitate .
so far we have not seen anything . "
china 's tourism revenue to reach 487.4 billion yuan in 2003
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 22 ( reporter sun yubo ) it is estimated that china 's tourism industry 's international and domestic incomes will be 487.4 billion yuan in 2003 , a 12.4 percent decrease from the previous year , but its performance will be better than expected .
according to the national tourism administration , the number of inbound tourists reached 91 million in 2003 , of which 11.3 million were foreigners , 32.7 million came into the country overnight , and 17.3 billion dollars were foreign exchange earnings .
the number of domestic tourists decreased by 0.9 percent and 11.2 percent , respectively , from the previous year .
a relevant person in charge of the national tourism administration said that in 2004 , the entire tourist industry will strive for the full recovery of the inbound tourism market , continue to promote the flourishing and development of the domestic tourist market , and carry out in depth the work of rectifying and rectifying the tourist market order .
at the same time , it is necessary to run well the theme of the " common people 's livelihood sightseeing year , " with the focus on the theme of " people 's livelihood touring , " and concentrate on planning and introducing a number of new tourist products that reflect the livelihood of the chinese people .
( international ) economists predict us dollar devaluation
xinhua news agency , davos , switzerland , january 23 ( reporters li jie , ding xigang ) - the 34 th annual meeting of the world economic forum currently held in davos , switzerland discussed the issue of the trend of depreciation of the us dollar on the 23 rd . some experts predict that the united states will be the biggest winner in the continued decline of the us dollar exchange rate .
most economists attending the meeting believe that us officials , including us secretary of the treasury john snow , seem to have given up the " strong dollar policy " pursued in recent years .
the low dollar will provide the united states with greater room for economic development and more jobs , which is clearly reflected in the manufacturing sector .
at the same time , the depreciation of the us dollar has made us products more competitive on the domestic and international markets , and this will help the united states fill its trade deficit .
however , experts believe that a weak dollar will also have an unfavorable impact on the united states .
first , the us stock market is likely to remain sluggish , the value of all kinds of investments will decrease , foreign investors will withdraw their funds because of worries that the dollar will fall further , and import commodities will become more expensive , which will eventually lead to a decline in the living standards of americans , and third , a drastic devaluation of the us dollar may trigger trade and financial turmoil .
however , the depreciation of the us dollar has dealt a more serious blow to europe , japan , and canada .
the european economy is facing the danger of an all - round decline as a result of the fall in the dollar 's foreign exchange rate .
china will accelerate the development of electronic products in the areas of automobile , medical , and other applications
xinhua news agency , beijing , january 26 ( reporter feng xiaofang ) china will speed up the development of various kinds of applied electronic products , such as automotive electronics , machine tool electronics , transportation electronics , and medical electronics , so as to expand the space for the development of the electronic information industry and satisfy the needs of various industries .
a relevant person in charge of the ministry of information industry said : to transform and upgrade traditional enterprises is one of the key tasks in popularizing the application of information technology .
promoting the application of information technology in all trades and professions and raising the market share of domestic products and equipment is necessary not only for transforming and upgrading traditional industries but also for bringing about rare development opportunities for the electronic information industry .
it has been learned that while expanding the space for the development of the electronic information industry and meeting the needs of various industries , it is also necessary to support the establishment of a public technological service capacity system and support research and development companies with actual strength in providing technological standards and testing environments to provide technical support and support for the application of information technology in key industries .
at the same time , develop technology service , management consulting , and system integration businesses ; support a number of service enterprises that provide systematic integration service , including application service providers , and promote the development of a new type of information service industry .
( international ) japan 's imports and exports hit record high in 2003
xinhua news agency , tokyo , january 26 ( reporter : yue shaoyan ) - according to statistics released by the japanese finance ministry on the 26th , japan 's import and export trade volume hit a record high in 2003 , with a trade surplus again breaking the 10 trillion japanese yen mark in three years .
in exports , japan 's exports to the united states decreased 9.8 percent from a year earlier , but its exports to asia rose 12.9 percent .
this not only made up for the decrease in japanese exports to the united states , but also resulted in a 4.7 percent increase in japanese exports last year , reaching a record 54.589 trillion yen .
with regard to imports , japan 's total import volume in 2003 increased by 5 percent over the previous year due to increased demand for oil and natural gas and rising prices , reaching a record high of 44.32021 trillion yen .
in 2003 , japan 's trade surplus stood at 10.2387 trillion yen , up 3.6 percent from the previous year , and again broke the 10 trillion yen mark three years ago .
number of private enterprises in guangdong exceeds state - owned and controlled enterprises for the first time
xinhua news agency , guangzhou , january 26 ( chen jiwu , hu yanni ) - according to information from the guangdong industrial and commercial administration bureau , the actual number of private enterprises in guangdong exceeded that of state - owned and their holding enterprises for the first time in 2003 , and domestic enterprises were effectively readjusted .
according to statistics , as of the end of 2003 , there were a total of 690,000 various kinds of enterprises ( including domestic and private enterprises and foreign - invested enterprises ) in the province , an increase of 0.59 percent over the end of the previous year .
among the total , 3.16 million were domestic enterprises , down 16.4 percent from the end of last year , with registered capital of 11,902 billion yuan , up 0.9 percent , private enterprises increasing 32.23 million yuan , and registered capital of 452.8 billion yuan , up 24.9 percent and 33.8 percent respectively .
the actual number of private enterprises exceeded that of state - owned and controlled enterprises for the first time .
although the number of state - owned and controlled enterprises has decreased in the course of structural adjustment , their actual strength has gradually increased , and their average registered capital ( funds ) reached 3.76 million yuan , up 20 percentage points from the end of 2002 .
according to statistics , in 2003 , there were a total of 10.05 million newly registered enterprises across the province , showing a decline of one or two points .
among them , the number of domestic - funded enterprises dropped 17.6 percent from the same period last year , while the number of private enterprises and foreign - invested enterprises was 6,561 , up 29 percent and 0.08 percent respectively .
the number of domestic , private , and foreign - invested enterprises accounted for 16 : 78 : 6 respectively of the total number of newly registered enterprises .
( international ) wto has referred the " bird subsidy " dispute to arbitration for settlement
xinhua news agency , geneva , january 26 ( reporter li jie ) the world trade organization announced on the 26th that the european union and seven other wto members have filed an appeal to the arbitration organization to impose sanctions on the united states for " bird subsidies " .
the appeal stems from the fact that the united states is unable to scrap the " byrd amendment " within the wto deadline .
the " byrd amendment " passed by the us congress in 2000 demanded that the us government give direct subsidies to those us companies whose interests were harmed in the antidumping and antisubsidy cases , instead of paying them to the us treasury .
this move of the united states has met with opposition from major trade partners , including the european union and japan .
the wto finally determined in january 2003 that the amendment was in violation of global trade rules and demanded that the united states repeal it by 27 december that year .
however , the united states has not enforced the wto 's decisions .
to this end , the european union , japan , canada , brazil , india , the republic of korea , mexico , and chile recently submitted applications to the wto asking for permission to levy additional tariffs on some products from the united states , which are equivalent to the amount of us government subsidies .
however , the united states subsequently questioned the extent of the sanctions and the legality of the complaint .
( hong kong , macao and taiwan ) hong kong spring festival retail business up 10%
xinhua news agency , hong kong , january 28 - according to the hong kong retail management association , retail sales in hong kong have been good during the lunar new year holidays . industry feedback shows that the average business volume has increased by 10 percent , and individual stores have increased by 20 to 30 percent .
yu peng , chairman of the hong kong retail management association , said a few days ago that the individual visit of mainland tourists to hong kong has brought along an atmosphere of consumption in hong kong . during the spring festival this year , the retail sales in hong kong are ideal . some industries such as jewellery and clothing have increased by 20 to 30 percent , and tourists from the mainland account for about 10 percent of the total business volume .
he said that the use of rmb cards in hong kong by mainland tourists has noticeably stimulated the spring festival market , with each signing account reaching 3,000 yuan on average and individual mainland tourists spending as much as 10,000 yuan .
last year , affected by sars , hong kong 's total retail sales declined by 4 percent .
mr yu estimated that with the recovery of the economy , there would be a median growth in the total retail business in hong kong this year , but prices of goods would also be under upward pressure due to higher costs .
he believed that hong kong 's deflation would improve this year .
denmark introduces new bill to limit immigrants
xinhua news agency , stockholm , january 28 , the danish government presented a new bill on restricting immigrants to the parliament on the 28 th .
under the bill , children born in denmark will no longer enjoy the right to automatically obtain the danish nationality .
the bill is the latest step taken by danish liberal party leader rasmussen since he became prime minister in november 2001 .
it is reported that the bill is likely to be passed by parliament because the liberal party has the support of the right - wing danish people 's party on the issue of immigration .
the bill requires all children born in denmark to apply for nationality , not nationality automatically , in the same way as other immigrants .
immigrants who have obtained nationality will be deprived of nationality for criminal charges that seriously endanger society .
in the past two years , the danish government has adopted a series of measures to limit the issuance of long - term resident permits and the entry of migrants into denmark .
the number of foreign asylum seekers in denmark dropped from 1,4347 in 1993 to 3,500 in 2003 .
as a result , denmark 's reputation as a free and human rights country has been damaged .
singapore 's achievements cannot be taken as a matter of course .
even if science and technology are developed further , i do not believe that people can maintain an ideal environment for a higher standard of living and a better quality of life , employment for all the people , and a constant increase in wages without hard work , social discipline , and adjustment to change .
these beautiful things can never be realized naturally .
only when all people understand that they must attach importance to their collective interests , make difficult compromises and make necessary adjustments can they have a better future .
what will singapore do in one or two decades ?
we all hope to see the future , but it is hard to predict it .
many factors are not controlled by singapore .
the development of many things is determined by the development of the world situation .
we do n't know when problems will occur , often involving gas .
for instance , three singapore tourists traveled to hong kong , and as a result they were infected with the salts virus . this is beyond any prediction .
in less than a month after the spring festival , three extraordinarily serious safety incidents have occurred in china , killing dozens of people every time .
people are shocked by the high frequency of accidents and the heavy losses of lives .
several months ago , several hundred people were killed in a gas pipe well - drilling in chongqing , a gas explosion in several coal mines , and a frequent fatal traffic accident .
china has a vast territory and a dense population , and the probability of disasters occurring is greater than that in other countries . it will lead to the death of tens of people or even hundreds of people , and this is a reality that there is no alternative in objective conditions .
however , from the perspective of general knowledge , china 's death toll is still too high .
most of the disasters were fires , coal explosions , explosions at firecrackers plants , and passenger transportation accidents .
this shows at least two problems : one is that safety measures are the most weak , and the other is that people have not drawn lessons from previous tragedies , thus causing similar accidents to occur again and again .
while singapore 's economy was growing at a high speed in the past , serious fires have also occurred . the painful memory of those fires has remained profound , but it has also rapidly raised singapore 's awareness of safety in public places .
china is also in a period of rapid economic growth and great social transformation .
the accident in which foreign domestic helpers were working in hong kong occurred frequently . although the figure was not as high as the number , according to the relative safety environment of the domestic helper , the number of accidents arising from the fall of domestic helpers was far from being in line with the minimal work nature of the number of casualties .
according to the statistics , 99 female domestic helpers from january 1999 to june 2003 died after the accident .
behind these figures are broken families that cannot wait for their daughter and mother to come home one by one , and at the same time , it is also an inevitable misfortune that we must exert every effort to reduce the number of regrets to the minimum direction of endeavor .
since 1999 , 96 indonesian domestic helpers have lost their lives while working in singapore , with some of them falling to work on high - rise buildings , according to a statement issued by the indonesian embassy .
the indonesian government has repeatedly expressed dissatisfaction over the fall of a female domestic helper , and has formulated new regulations to more strictly control the quality of local indonesian domestic helpers and to protect their safety , but the problem has yet to be resolved .
it cannot help feeling deeply puzzled by the fact that the number of women and domestic helpers who fell to work on construction sites is even higher than the number of casualties . this can not but cause people to think deeply about the background and cause of the accident .
chen kong - li , a well - known expert on the taiwan issue on the chinese mainland at home and abroad , recently published a new book entitled " observe taiwan . "
most of the articles in the book have been written after taiwan 's first change of political parties in march 2000 . by the time chen shui - bian put forward the theory of " one country , two systems , " the author observed and considered taiwan 's domestic situation and cross - strait relations during his " observation of his words and deeds . "
the articles written two years ago were published two years later . this shows that the mainland 's process of examining taiwan - related studies was very complicated and took a long time to go . this shows even more that the " observation of taiwan " was not easily come by .
for a long time , while observing and studying the taiwan issue , chen kong - li always sought truth from facts , sought truth from facts , was not restricted by any subjective pre - set political framework , and worked hard to explore zhuo 's profound insight .
this feature has impressed people even more deeply after reading this book .
since the early 1980s , the research on the taiwan issue has become an " epoch - making activity " on the mainland . various research institutes have appeared one after another . various kinds of scholars and experts have also displayed their talents .
overseas , people generally split the mainland 's taiwan research institutes into the northern and southern factions .
the stand of the northern faction is relatively close to the government , and its speeches are relatively hard - line . in the course of development of certain specific historical stages or major political events , it shows relatively more overbearing hawks ' color .
the taiwan research institute sent to the south is mainly distributed to areas south of the yangtze river , including shanghai and fujian .
