the post of post of japan confirmed to the education office of the university of london that koizumi only attended a few courses in britain for nine months , and he did not get any degree either .
china 's large and medium - sized media vied with one another to report and download this scandal so that the broad masses of compatriots can express their joy .
indeed , the prime minister of a country has gone so far as to fabricate false academic qualifications to deceive the people of his country .
