however , if we can change a perspective , perhaps we can see some positive significance from this scandal .
moreover , these positive things are precisely what we lack and we need to improve .
in recent years , we have always advocated " honesty , " " building a sunshine government , " respecting the public 's " right to know , " and enhancing the " transparency " of administration . however , facts are far from ideal .
think about this , the diploma of a state 's prime minister was " mixed with water " and was not that big event in the first place , but it was exposed by the media and was in hot pursuit and fierce attack .
what else can such a country not be " sunshine ? "
at the taiwan election publicity variety show , all major camps will use tourist buses to transport the masses to the venue . however , the recent situation is that the evening party of chen shui - bian and annette lu has clearly been much more cold - shouldered compared with the evening party of lien chan and james soong .
when taiwan president chen shui - bian [ ch'en shui - pien ] went to a certain place in the north not long ago to shout " freeze garlic ( election ) , " half of the people in taiwan went so far as to cry about face - saving .
if there is no accident , taiwan 's presidential election , as it enters the countdown countdown period , and judging from the poll results and signs of an underground check , can all be assumed that the chen - lu meeting will be defeated .
